Quantization
- Before: 4-bit NF4 (QLoRA) always
- Now: bf16 by default; --load_in_4bit flag for low-VRAM
LoRA rank
- Before: r=16, alpha=32
- Now: r=32 (configurable via --lora_r), alpha=64
LoRA modules
- Before: q, k, v, o only
- Now: + gate, up, down (MLP projections)
Gradient checkpointing
- Before: always enabled
- Now: removed


Batch size
- Before: 1
- Now: 4
Grad accumulation
- Before: 8
- Now: 4
Effective batch
- Before: 8
- Now: 16
max_length
- Before: 3072 (already set)
- Now: 3072
New arg
- Before: —
- Now: --lora_r 32
